con:testCase.name: 5.1.1 Lägg till ett engagemang till en producent

con:configuration.scriptText: import se.skl.rivta.tksupport.soapui.ContentAssertions def ca = new ContentAssertions(context, messageExchange, log) ca.assertNonEmptyResponse() ca.assertSpecificValueInAnyRecord('/fc1:engagement/urn1:logicalAddress', "SKLTP-MOCK01") ca.assertElementExistsInAllRecords('/fc1:engagement/urn1:creationTime') ca.assertSpecificValueInAllRecords('/fc1:engagement/urn1:mostRecentContent', context.expand('${#TestSuite#mostRecentContent}')) ca.assertExactNumberOfRecords(1)
